It only checks for the syntax (whether the code is valid or not) and dont check the format.
$terraform validate
It formate the code or allign the code properly.
$terraform fmt
It will show you which things are going to create
$terraform plan
It will get save your output of terraform plan in sample.txt file
$tarraform plan -out sample.txt
(+) is for addition
(-) is for delete
(~) is for changes
